Privacy Policy
This Privacy Policy outlines how shareclub ("we," "us," or "our") collects, uses, and protects the personal information of users ("you" or "your") of our website and mobile application (collectively referred to as "the Service"). We are committed to respecting your privacy rights and ensuring the security of your personal information. Please read this Privacy Policy carefully to understand how we handle your information.
Information We Collect
a. Personal Information: We may collect personal information that you voluntarily provide to us, such as your name, email address, phone number, and other contact details when you register for an account, place an order, or communicate with us.
b. Usage Data: We automatically collect certain information about your interactions with the Service, including your IP address, device information, browser type, and browsing history.
Use of Information
a. Provide and Improve the Service: We use your personal information to provide the Service, process your orders, respond to your inquiries, and improve the functionality and user experience of our website and app.
b. Communication: We may use your contact information to send you important updates, promotional materials, and newsletters related to our products and services. You can opt out of these communications at any time.
c. Analytics and Research: We may analyse the usage data to gain insights into user behaviour, improve our products and services, and conduct research to enhance the effectiveness of our platform.
Data Sharing
a. Third-Party Service Providers: We may share your personal information with trusted third-party service providers who assist us in operating our business, such as payment processors, shipping partners, and customer support services. These providers are contractually obligated to protect your information and use it solely for the purposes specified by us.
b. Legal Compliance: We may disclose your personal information if required to do so by law or in response to a valid request from a governmental authority.
Data Security
We take appropriate measures to protect your personal information from unauthorised access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. However, no method of transmission or storage over the internet is completely secure. Therefore, we cannot guarantee absolute security of your information.
Your Rights and Choices
a. Access and Update: You have the right to access and update your personal information in our records. You may do so by logging into your account or contacting us directly.
b. Opt-Out: You can opt out of receiving promotional emails by following the instructions provided in the communication. However, we may still send you essential service-related communications.
Children's Privacy
The Service is not intended for individuals under the age of 16. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If we become aware that we have collected personal information from a child without parental consent, we will take steps to delete that information.
Changes to the Privacy Policy
We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on our website, and the revised policy will become effective upon posting. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any updates.
Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns regarding these Privacy Policy, please contact us at support@weareshareclub.com
Last updated: 29/05/2023